page.title: 20ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS-HOLKER MOSS
page.content: The information about the Holker Moss area has been collected by G.C.E. Geography students of Ulverston Victoria High School.They are:- Tony Bibby,Matthew Bramall,Ian Cockshott,Craig Davidson,Robert Dickinson,Toby Hadwin,Duncan Hall, Stuart Harrison,Matthew Hind,Roger Howell,Nigel Hunt,James Jackson, Richard Johnson,Simon Lawson,Robert Luscombe,Peter Marsh,Jeremy Park,Robin Parkinson,Laurence Peel,Paul Robley, Roy Postlethwaite,Julian Ronald,Nathan Wood,Jill Anderson,Sarah Graveston, Avril Ramsay,Susan Smith,Yvonne Smith, Rosemary Vendy under the guidance of Mr.Trevor Boyt. Help and cooperation was obtained from Holker Estates Co.Ltd.,Bigland Hall Sporting Estates,the Nature Conservancey,Mrs.Croasdell and other local inhabitants.
